<p>Arch Linux 的镜像配置文件在 <strong>/etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</strong>，里面一般涵盖了国内的镜像源。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># vim /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>搜索 China，将其中一个 Server 放在头部即可。</p>